{"tid":1178834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★IT?】傳滙豐擬裁員至少500人，又指是次的裁員計劃僅屬冰山一角","createTime":"2019-05-30T16:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T03:44:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0992d280feb71c7944a5045942ce53224cfd41","tid":1178834,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"滙豐控股(00005)再爆大規模裁員消息，外電引述消息人士指，滙控行政總裁范寧向集團高層施壓，正計劃削減數百個投資銀行的職位，環球銀行及市場業務更擬裁最少500職位，以減低營運成本壓力。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，正式裁員人數尚未有定案，預計最快於今年6月中旬開始裁員。又指是<span style=\"color: red;\">次的裁員計劃僅屬冰山一角</span>，意味早前傳出為削減開支的「橡樹計劃」，已重新啟動並進入新階段。<br />\n<br />\n外電引述滙控聲明指，集團恒常地重新評估各業務及部門的需要，以確員工在合適的地方，擔當適當的職位。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐發言人回覆《東網》查詢時表示不予評論。<br />\n<br />\n滙控集團財務總監邵偉信在5月初公布首季業績時，曾表明努力控制營運開支增速，但強調不應視裁員為開源節流唯一手段，更澄清早前盛傳用作節省成本的「橡樹計劃」屬傳聞，集團未有大規模裁員需要。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190530/bkn-20190530210050165-0530_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190530%2Fbkn-20190530210050165-0530_00842_001.html&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=4177e69e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190530/bkn-20190530210050165-0530_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"62266284c13c36ab1404d629397c815d48853669","tid":1178834,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"IT first<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94751ec464aa2c18a8328d62b39e3f45c3771746","tid":1178834,"uid":76747,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:29:13.000Z","msg":"班IT佬應該買匯豐做對沖<br />\n被炒後仍有息收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb65d399f244d3d4b828bbd97f921456eb289b5","tid":1178834,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:37:33.000Z","msg":"IT唔會有500人咁多，應該包括好多部門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241e2af112d6d7b1f1e7dab7b26d11d2f9bf6187","tid":1178834,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94751ec464aa2c18a8328d62b39e3f45c3771746","tid":1178834,"uid":76747,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:29:13.000Z","msg":"班IT佬應該買匯豐做對沖<br />\n被炒後仍有息收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942dbc9b6835873b28fe312b0424f9d8021b4203","tid":1178834,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"早幾年話總部設香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81af70787f8576452a2313eb5dae25b1077e422e","tid":1178834,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"942dbc9b6835873b28fe312b0424f9d8021b4203","tid":1178834,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"早幾年話總部設香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"搬撚左去巴黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce09ca974761ed439f77ffdcbfd092ae178b34a","tid":1178834,"uid":166947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dbb65d399f244d3d4b828bbd97f921456eb289b5","tid":1178834,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:37:33.000Z","msg":"IT唔會有500人咁多，應該包括好多部門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"it點會無500人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實炒IT成日講笑咁講，但係IT依幾年cut得唔係最勁<br />\n<br />\n炒得最勁係早幾年大搖大擺咁係咁請人果啲risk, compliance友<br />\n<br />\nIT已經cut無可cut<br />\n<br />\n題外話，基本上每次大貓restructure,即係將10個位demise,再開番7個新post<br />\n相比之下細貓有同情味好多 &mdash; 當然代價就係所有人嘅人工都平均地低一截"},{"pid":"8e87595b1151707426da4505ff991895ca6cfae0","tid":1178834,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3893b04f74bc23710b4829d3d4f85ee80af3feab","tid":1178834,"uid":52605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:29:16.000Z","msg":"一間用香港做名賺鳩香港人錢嘅英國銀行<br />\n次次抄人都揀香港先<br />\n香港銀行啲門面仲要寫敵國殘字<br />\n仲要先過中資銀行喺自己設計嘅銀紙奶共<br />\n其實都好仆街"},{"pid":"e1898d0a2c6d9d54fdf8a9c220768311480ff542","tid":1178834,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62266284c13c36ab1404d629397c815d48853669","tid":1178834,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"IT first<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:44:40.000Z","msg":"似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}